data.name: Terra Firma Gravity
data.desc: During your opponent's Battle Phase, if you control "Elemental HERO Terra Firma": This turn, all Level 4 or lower monsters your opponent controls that can attack a face-up "Elemental HERO Terra Firma" you control must attack it, and cannot otherwise attack.
